gative journalism. It allows you to be the expert in your own life.The AREA Method provides you with:*Defined tasks that guide and focus your research on your vision of success;*A structure that isolates your sources, giving you insight into their perspectives, biases and incentives;*Investigative resources, tips and techniques to upgrade your research and analysis beyond document-based sources;*Exercises to foster creativity and originality in your thinking;*A sequence and framework that brings your disparate pieces of research together to build your confidence and conviction about your financial decision.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aDecision makingxMethodologyvProblems, exercises, etc. 0aFinancexDecision makingxMethodology. 0aFinancexResearchxMethodology. 0aResearchxMethodologyvProblems, exercises, etc. 4aBusiness (General). 4aGeneral Economics.  aAREA method, financial investigations, investment analysis, financial decision-making, incentives, framework.1 aBlair, Tony, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065198008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2019z9783110606065oZDB-23-DBV08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Law & Social Sciences 2019 ENGz978311061013040uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150173095540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501730955423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501730955/original  a978-3-11-061013-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Law & Soc